<subSubSection id="518035954032FFAD0FCBF825FD7BF882" lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="101" pageId="0" pageNumber="100" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="1925661E4032FFAC0FCBF825FF73F878" blockId="0.[136,1452,1551,2044]" pageId="0" pageNumber="100">
<emphasis id="2BEEBA0C4032FFAC0FCBF825FED7F837" bold="true" box="[189,321,1947,1971]" pageId="0" pageNumber="100">Comments:</emphasis>
Range of measurements of apical axis is greater than the original description (5-8.75 µm) and range of pervalvar axis is smaller (12.5-20 µm). Direction of seta of the convex valve is at less angle comparing to the drawings of the 
<typeStatus id="C621D8BC4032FFAC0FD9F85AFF76F878" box="[175,224,2020,2044]" pageId="0" pageNumber="100">type</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<caption id="4DE536964033FFAD0FFEFCF9FF63FC22" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501332" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6501332" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6501332/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="101" startId="1.[136,243,839,861]" targetBox="[340,1247,188,813]" targetPageId="1">
